metadata.name: serious future sadness generations
metadata.description:
Procedurally generated 8K 3D render of hybrid anatomical bone structure of curious origin.

Geometry, textures, renders, and final composite generated purely from custom python pipeline controlling Houdini, RizomUV, Substance Designer, Redshift, and Deadline to create variations based on string input.

Piece title = random seed

process_01.py -r 8192 -s "serious future sadness generations"
